    <item>
      <title>嘉能可首席执行官预计钴供应过剩将持续两年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/glencore-ceo-sees-cobalt-glut-lasting-as-long-as-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球第二大钴矿商嘉能可 (Glencore Plc) 表示，由于新增产量超过需求，市场供应过剩局面可能延续到 2026 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/glencore-ceo-sees-cobalt-glut-lasting-as-long-as-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:37:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰银行首席执行官因未解释离职原因接受质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/abn-amro-ceo-grilled-over-missing-explanation-for-his-departure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰银行 (ABN Amro Bank NV) 首席执行官罗伯特·斯瓦克 (Robert Swaak) 上周决定辞职，这让这家荷兰银行的盈利情况黯然失色，投资者和记者向他提出了大量问题，而他大多都避而不答。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/abn-amro-ceo-grilled-over-missing-explanation-for-his-departure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:35:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的美国比特币储备计划引起没收专家的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/trump-s-plan-for-us-bitcoin-stockpile-alarms-forfeiture-experts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在竞选时承诺利用美国政府持有的加密货币建立国家比特币储备，这引起了前检察官的担忧，他们表示，此举将转移扣押的数字资产，而这些资产原本可用于补偿犯罪受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/trump-s-plan-for-us-bitcoin-stockpile-alarms-forfeiture-experts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德资产利润上升，资产规模达到约 1 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/brookfield-asset-management-profits-rise-assets-hit-1-trillion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司 (Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.) 报告季度利润增长，并表示其管理的资产增至创纪录的约 1 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/brookfield-asset-management-profits-rise-assets-hit-1-trillion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国抵押贷款利率跌至 6.55%，创两年来最大降幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-mortgage-rates-tumble-to-6-55-in-biggest-drop-in-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国30年期抵押贷款利率上周出现两年来最大跌幅，达到2023年5月以来的最低水平，并引发再融资申请激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-mortgage-rates-tumble-to-6-55-in-biggest-drop-in-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
